254.sql: WITH elementpaircounts AS (SELECT t1.element || '-' || t3.element AS element_pair, COUNT(*) AS pair_count FROM connected INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON connected.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t3 ON connected.atom_id2 = t3.atom_id GROUP BY t1.element, t3.element), mostcommonelementpair AS (SELECT element_pair FROM elementpaircounts ORDER BY pair_count DESC LIMIT 1) SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN t1.element || '-' || t3.element = mce.element_pair THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(*) FROM connected INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON connected.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t3 ON connected.atom_id2 = t3.atom_id CROSS JOIN mostcommonelementpair AS mce

SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN t1.element || '-' || t3.element = (SELECT t1.element || '-' || t3.element FROM connected INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON connected.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t3 ON connected.atom_id2 = t3.atom_id GROUP BY t1.element, t3.element ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(*) FROM connected INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON connected.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t3 ON connected.atom_id2 = t3.atom_id

SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN t1.element || '-' || t3.element = (SELECT t1.element || '-' || t3.element AS element_pair FROM connected INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON connected.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t3 ON connected.atom_id2 = t3.atom_id GROUP BY t1.element, t3.element ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(*) FROM connected INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON connected.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t3 ON connected.atom_id2 = t3.atom_id

SELECT CAST(common_count AS REAL) * 100 / total_count AS percentage FROM (SELECT COUNT(*) AS common_count FROM bond AS t1 INNER JOIN connected AS t2 ON t1.bond_id = t2.bond_id INNER JOIN atom AS t3 ON t2.atom_id = t3.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t4 ON t2.atom_id2 = t4.atom_id WHERE (t3.element, t4.element) = (SELECT element1, element2 FROM (SELECT t3.element AS element1, t4.element AS element2, COUNT(*) AS count FROM bond AS t1 INNER JOIN connected AS t2 ON t1.bond_id = t2.bond_id INNER JOIN atom AS t3 ON t2.atom_id = t3.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t4 ON t2.atom_id2 = t4.atom_id GROUP BY element1, element2 ORDER BY count DESC LIMIT 1))) AS common_bonds CROSS JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_count FROM bond) AS total_bonds

SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN t.element_combination = (SELECT element_combination FROM (SELECT t1.element || '-' || t2.element AS element_combination, COUNT(*) AS cnt FROM atom AS t1 INNER JOIN connected AS c ON t1.atom_id = c.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON c.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id GROUP BY t1.element || '-' || t2.element ORDER BY cnt DESC LIMIT 1)) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / NULLIF(COUNT(*), 0) AS percentage FROM (SELECT t1.element || '-' || t2.element AS element_combination FROM atom AS t1 INNER JOIN connected AS c ON t1.atom_id = c.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON c.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id) AS t

SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN t.element_combination = (SELECT element_combination FROM (SELECT t1.element || '-' || t2.element AS element_combination, COUNT(*) AS cnt FROM atom AS t1 INNER JOIN connected AS c ON t1.atom_id = c.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON c.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id GROUP BY t1.element || '-' || t2.element ORDER BY cnt DESC LIMIT 1)) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(*) AS percentage FROM (SELECT t1.element || '-' || t2.element AS element_combination FROM atom AS t1 INNER JOIN connected AS c ON t1.atom_id = c.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON c.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id) AS t

SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN t.element || '_' || t2.element = (SELECT element1 || '_' || element2 FROM (SELECT t.element AS element1, t2.element AS element2, COUNT(*) AS cnt FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS t ON c.atom_id = t.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON c.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id GROUP BY t.element, t2.element ORDER BY cnt DESC LIMIT 1)) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(*) AS percentage FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS t ON c.atom_id = t.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON c.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id

SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN combination_count = (SELECT MAX(combination_count) FROM (SELECT element1, element2, COUNT(*) AS combination_count FROM (SELECT t1.element AS element1, t2.element AS element2 FROM connected INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON connected.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON connected.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id) AS element_pairs GROUP BY element1, element2) AS max_combinations) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM connected) AS percentage FROM (SELECT element1, element2, COUNT(*) AS combination_count FROM (SELECT t1.element AS element1, t2.element AS element2 FROM connected INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON connected.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON connected.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id) AS element_pairs GROUP BY element1, element2) AS combinations

SELECT CAST(MAX(combination_count) AS REAL) * 100 / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM connected) AS percentage FROM (SELECT element1, element2, COUNT(*) AS combination_count FROM (SELECT t1.element AS element1, t2.element AS element2 FROM connected INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON connected.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON connected.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id) AS element_pairs GROUP BY element1, element2) AS combinations

WITH elementpairs AS (SELECT a1.element AS element1, a2.element AS element2, COUNT(c.bond_id) AS pair_count FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS a1 ON c.atom_id = a1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS a2 ON c.atom_id2 = a2.atom_id GROUP BY a1.element, a2.element), mostcommonpair AS (SELECT element1, element2 FROM elementpairs ORDER BY pair_count DESC LIMIT 1) SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN a1.element = mcp.element1 AND a2.element = mcp.element2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(c.bond_id) AS percentage FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS a1 ON c.atom_id = a1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS a2 ON c.atom_id2 = a2.atom_id CROSS JOIN mostcommonpair AS mcp

SELECT (most_common.most_common_cnt / total.total_bonds) * 100 AS percentage FROM (SELECT t1.element AS element1, t2.element AS element2, COUNT(*) AS most_common_cnt FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON c.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON c.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id GROUP BY t1.element, t2.element ORDER BY most_common_cnt DESC LIMIT 1) AS most_common INNER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_bonds FROM connected) AS total ON TRUE

SELECT CAST(most_common.most_common_cnt AS REAL) * 100 / total.total_bonds AS percentage FROM (SELECT t1.element AS element1, t2.element AS element2, COUNT(*) AS most_common_cnt FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON c.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON c.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id GROUP BY t1.element, t2.element ORDER BY most_common_cnt DESC LIMIT 1) AS most_common INNER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_bonds FROM connected) AS total ON TRUE

SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN (t1.element, t2.element) = (SELECT t1.element, t2.element FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON c.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON c.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id GROUP BY t1.element, t2.element ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(*) AS percentage FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON c.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON c.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id

SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN (a1.element, a2.element) = (SELECT a1.element, a2.element FROM connected AS c2 INNER JOIN atom AS a1 ON c2.atom_id = a1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS a2 ON c2.atom_id2 = a2.atom_id GROUP BY a1.element, a2.element ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(*) AS percentage FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS a1 ON c.atom_id = a1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS a2 ON c.atom_id2 = a2.atom_id

SELECT CAST((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM connected AS c JOIN atom AS a1 ON c.atom_id = a1.atom_id JOIN atom AS a2 ON c.atom_id2 = a2.atom_id WHERE (a1.element, a2.element) = (SELECT a1.element, a2.element FROM atom AS a1 JOIN connected AS c ON a1.atom_id = c.atom_id JOIN atom AS a2 ON c.atom_id2 = a2.atom_id GROUP BY a1.element, a2.element ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1)) AS REAL) * 100 / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM bond) AS percentage

WITH elementcombinations AS (SELECT a1.element AS element1, a2.element AS element2, COUNT(c.bond_id) AS combination_count FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS a1 ON c.atom_id = a1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS a2 ON c.atom_id2 = a2.atom_id GROUP BY a1.element, a2.element ORDER BY combination_count DESC LIMIT 1), mostcommonbonds AS (SELECT COUNT(c.bond_id) AS most_common_count FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS a1 ON c.atom_id = a1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS a2 ON c.atom_id2 = a2.atom_id WHERE (a1.element, a2.element) = (SELECT element1, element2 FROM elementcombinations)) SELECT (mc.most_common_count * 100.0 / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM bond)) AS percentage FROM mostcommonbonds AS mc

WITH elementcombinations AS (SELECT a1.element AS element1, a2.element AS element2, COUNT(c.bond_id) AS combination_count FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS a1 ON c.atom_id = a1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS a2 ON c.atom_id2 = a2.atom_id GROUP BY a1.element, a2.element ORDER BY combination_count DESC LIMIT 1), mostcommonbonds AS (SELECT COUNT(c.bond_id) AS most_common_count FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS a1 ON c.atom_id = a1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS a2 ON c.atom_id2 = a2.atom_id WHERE (a1.element, a2.element) = (SELECT element1, element2 FROM elementcombinations)) SELECT (mc.most_common_count * 100.0 / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM bond)) AS percentage FROM mostcommonbonds AS mc

WITH elementpairs AS (SELECT a1.element AS element1, a2.element AS element2, COUNT(*) AS count FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS a1 ON c.atom_id = a1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS a2 ON c.atom_id2 = a2.atom_id GROUP BY a1.element, a2.element), maxelementpair AS (SELECT element1, element2, count FROM elementpairs WHERE count = (SELECT MAX(count) FROM elementpairs)) SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN a1.element = maxelementpair.element1 AND a2.element = maxelementpair.element2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(*) FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS a1 ON c.atom_id = a1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS a2 ON c.atom_id2 = a2.atom_id CROSS JOIN maxelementpair

SELECT CAST(COUNT(CASE WHEN t1.element || '_' || t3.element = (SELECT t1.element || '_' || t3.element AS combo FROM connected AS t2 INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON t2.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t3 ON t2.atom_id2 = t3.atom_id GROUP BY t1.element, t3.element ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1) THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(bond.bond_id) AS percentage FROM bond INNER JOIN connected AS t2 ON bond.bond_id = t2.bond_id INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON t2.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t3 ON t2.atom_id2 = t3.atom_id

SELECT (COUNT(*) * 100.0 / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM bond)) AS percentage FROM connected INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON connected.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON connected.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id WHERE (t1.element, t2.element) = (SELECT element1, element2 FROM (SELECT t1.element AS element1, t2.element AS element2, COUNT(*) AS combination_count FROM connected INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON connected.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON connected.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id GROUP BY element1, element2 ORDER BY combination_count DESC LIMIT 1))

SELECT CAST(COUNT(bond_id) AS REAL) * 100 / (SELECT COUNT(bond_id) FROM bond) AS percentage FROM connected INNER JOIN atom ON connected.atom_id = atom.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS atom2 ON connected.atom_id2 = atom2.atom_id GROUP BY atom.element, atom2.element HAVING COUNT(*) = (SELECT MAX(cnt) FROM (SELECT COUNT(*) AS cnt FROM connected INNER JOIN atom ON connected.atom_id = atom.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS atom2 ON connected.atom_id2 = atom2.atom_id GROUP BY atom.element, atom2.element))

WITH mostcommoncombination AS (SELECT t1.element AS element1, t2.element AS element2 FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON c.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON c.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id GROUP BY t1.element, t2.element ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1), countmostcommonbonds AS (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON c.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON c.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id WHERE (t1.element, t2.element) IN (SELECT element1, element2 FROM mostcommoncombination) OR (t2.element, t1.element) IN (SELECT element1, element2 FROM mostcommoncombination)), totalbonds AS (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM bond) SELECT CAST((SELECT * FROM countmostcommonbonds) AS REAL) * 100 / (SELECT * FROM totalbonds) AS percentage

WITH mostcommoncombination AS (SELECT t1.element AS element1, t2.element AS element2 FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON c.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON c.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id GROUP BY t1.element, t2.element ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1), countmostcommonbonds AS (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON c.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON c.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id WHERE (t1.element, t2.element) IN (SELECT element1, element2 FROM mostcommoncombination) OR (t2.element, t1.element) IN (SELECT element1, element2 FROM mostcommoncombination)), totalbonds AS (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM bond) SELECT CAST((SELECT * FROM countmostcommonbonds) AS REAL) * 100 / (SELECT * FROM totalbonds) AS percentage

WITH mostcommoncombination AS (SELECT t1.element AS element1, t2.element AS element2 FROM connected INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON connected.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON connected.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id GROUP BY t1.element, t2.element ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1), countmostcommonbonds AS (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM connected INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON connected.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON connected.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id WHERE (t1.element, t2.element) = (SELECT element1, element2 FROM mostcommoncombination)), totalbonds AS (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM connected) SELECT CAST((SELECT * FROM countmostcommonbonds) AS REAL) * 100 / (SELECT * FROM totalbonds) AS percentage

SELECT CAST(COUNT(CASE WHEN t1.element || t3.element = (SELECT t1.element || t3.element FROM atom AS t1 INNER JOIN connected AS t2 ON t1.atom_id = t2.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t3 ON t2.atom_id2 = t3.atom_id GROUP BY t1.element, t3.element ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1) THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(*) AS percentage FROM atom AS t1 INNER JOIN connected AS t2 ON t1.atom_id = t2.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t3 ON t2.atom_id2 = t3.atom_id

SELECT CAST(COUNT(CASE WHEN t1.element || t3.element = (SELECT t1.element || t3.element FROM atom AS t1 INNER JOIN connected AS t2 ON t1.atom_id = t2.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t3 ON t2.atom_id2 = t3.atom_id GROUP BY t1.element, t3.element ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1) THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(t4.bond_id) AS percentage FROM atom AS t1 INNER JOIN connected AS t2 ON t1.atom_id = t2.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t3 ON t2.atom_id2 = t3.atom_id INNER JOIN bond AS t4 ON t2.bond_id = t4.bond_id

SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN t1.combination = t2.most_common_combination THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(*) AS percentage FROM (SELECT a1.element || '-' || a2.element AS combination FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS a1 ON c.atom_id = a1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS a2 ON c.atom_id2 = a2.atom_id) AS t1 CROSS JOIN (SELECT a1.element || '-' || a2.element AS most_common_combination FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS a1 ON c.atom_id = a1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS a2 ON c.atom_id2 = a2.atom_id GROUP BY a1.element, a2.element ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1) AS t2

SELECT CAST(common_bonds AS REAL) * 100 / total_bonds FROM (SELECT COUNT(*) AS common_bonds FROM connected AS t3 INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON t1.atom_id = t3.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON t2.atom_id = t3.atom_id2 WHERE (t1.element, t2.element) = (SELECT element1, element2 FROM (SELECT t1.element AS element1, t2.element AS element2 FROM atom AS t1 INNER JOIN connected AS t3 ON t1.atom_id = t3.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON t2.atom_id = t3.atom_id2) GROUP BY element1, element2 ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1)) CROSS JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_bonds FROM bond)

WITH elementcombinations AS (SELECT t1.element || '_' || t2.element AS element_combination, COUNT(*) AS combination_count FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON c.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON c.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id GROUP BY element_combination), maxcombination AS (SELECT element_combination, combination_count FROM elementcombinations WHERE combination_count = (SELECT MAX(combination_count) FROM elementcombinations)), bondcount AS (SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_bonds FROM connected), commoncombinationbonds AS (SELECT COUNT(*) AS common_combination_bonds FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON c.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON c.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id INNER JOIN maxcombination AS mc ON t1.element || '_' || t2.element = mc.element_combination) SELECT CAST(common_combination_bonds AS REAL) * 100 / total_bonds AS percentage FROM commoncombinationbonds CROSS JOIN bondcount

SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN t1.element || '_' || t2.element = (SELECT t1.element || '_' || t2.element AS combo FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON c.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON c.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id GROUP BY t1.element, t2.element ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(*) FROM connected AS c INNER JOIN atom AS t1 ON c.atom_id = t1.atom_id INNER JOIN atom AS t2 ON c.atom_id2 = t2.atom_id

SELECT ((t3.balance_end - t3.balance_start) / t3.balance_start) * 100 AS increase_rate FROM loan AS t1 INNER JOIN disp AS t2 ON t1.account_id = t2.account_id INNER JOIN (SELECT account_id, MAX(CASE WHEN date = '1993-03-22' THEN balance END) AS balance_start, MAX(CASE WHEN date = '1998-12-27' THEN balance END) AS balance_end FROM trans GROUP BY account_id HAVING NOT balance_start IS NULL AND balance_start <> 0 AND NOT balance_end IS NULL) AS t3 ON t2.account_id = t3.account_id WHERE t1.date = '1993-07-05'

SELECT CASE WHEN NOT balance_1993 IS NULL AND NOT balance_1998 IS NULL THEN ((balance_1998 - balance_1993) / balance_1993) * 100 ELSE NULL END AS increase_rate FROM (SELECT MAX(CASE WHEN t1.date = '1993-03-22' THEN t1.balance END) AS balance_1993, MAX(CASE WHEN t1.date = '1998-12-27' THEN t1.balance END) AS balance_1998 FROM trans AS t1 INNER JOIN disp AS t2 ON t1.account_id = t2.account_id INNER JOIN account AS t3 ON t2.account_id = t3.account_id INNER JOIN loan AS t4 ON t3.account_id = t4.account_id WHERE STRFTIME('%Y-%m', t4.date) = '1993-07' AND t1.date IN ('1993-03-22', '1998-12-27')) AS balances

598.sql: SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN STRFTIME('%Y', badges.date) = '2010' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(badges.id) - CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN STRFTIME('%Y', badges.date) = '2011' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(badges.id) AS percentagedifference FROM badges WHERE badges.name = 'Student'

SELECT CAST(COUNT(CASE WHEN STRFTIME('%Y', badges.date) = '2010' THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(badges.id) - CAST(COUNT(CASE WHEN STRFTIME('%Y', badges.date) = '2011' THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(badges.id) AS percentagedifference FROM badges WHERE badges.name = 'Student'

SELECT ((SUM(CASE WHEN STRFTIME('%Y', date) = '2010' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(*)) - (SUM(CASE WHEN STRFTIME('%Y', date) = '2011' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(*))) AS percentage_difference FROM badges WHERE name = 'Student'

SELECT ((CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN STRFTIME('%Y', date) = '2010' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) / COUNT(*)) - (CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN STRFTIME('%Y', date) = '2011' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) / COUNT(*))) * 100 AS percentagedifference FROM badges WHERE name = 'Student'

SELECT ((CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN STRFTIME('%Y', date) = '2010' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) / COUNT(*)) * 100 - (CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN STRFTIME('%Y', date) = '2011' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) / COUNT(*)) * 100) AS percentage_difference FROM badges WHERE name = 'Student'

SELECT ((CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN STRFTIME('%Y', date) = '2010' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) / NULLIF(COUNT(*), 0)) * 100 - (CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN STRFTIME('%Y', date) = '2011' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) / NULLIF(COUNT(*), 0)) * 100) AS percentage_difference FROM badges WHERE name = 'Student'

94.sql: SELECT t1.account_id, ((SELECT MAX(a11) FROM district) - (SELECT MIN(a11) FROM district)) AS salary_gap FROM account AS t1 INNER JOIN disp AS t2 ON t1.account_id = t2.account_id INNER JOIN client AS t3 ON t2.client_id = t3.client_id INNER JOIN district AS t4 ON t1.district_id = t4.district_id WHERE t3.gender = 'F' AND t4.a11 = (SELECT MIN(a11) FROM district) ORDER BY t3.birth_date ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT t1.account_id, (max_salary - min_salary) AS salary_gap FROM account AS t1 INNER JOIN disp AS t2 ON t1.account_id = t2.account_id INNER JOIN client AS t3 ON t2.client_id = t3.client_id INNER JOIN district AS t4 ON t1.district_id = t4.district_id CROSS JOIN (SELECT MAX(a11) AS max_salary, MIN(a11) AS min_salary FROM district) AS salary_info WHERE t3.gender = 'F' AND t4.a11 = (SELECT MIN(a11) FROM district) AND t3.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F' AND district_id = t4.district_id)

SELECT t2.account_id, (SELECT MAX(a11) - MIN(a11) FROM district) AS salary_gap FROM (SELECT client_id, birth_date FROM client WHERE gender = 'F' AND district_id = (SELECT district_id FROM district ORDER BY a11 ASC LIMIT 1) ORDER BY birth_date ASC LIMIT 1) AS t1 INNER JOIN disp AS t2 ON t1.client_id = t2.client_id

SELECT a.account_id, (SELECT MAX(a11) - MIN(a11) FROM district) AS salary_gap FROM account AS a INNER JOIN disp AS d ON a.account_id = d.account_id INNER JOIN client AS c ON d.client_id = c.client_id INNER JOIN district AS dist ON c.district_id = dist.district_id WHERE c.gender = 'F' AND c.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F') AND dist.a11 = (SELECT MIN(a11) FROM district WHERE district_id IN (SELECT c.district_id FROM client AS c WHERE c.gender = 'F' AND c.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F')))

SELECT a.account_id, (SELECT MAX(a11) - MIN(a11) FROM district) AS salary_gap FROM account AS a INNER JOIN disp AS d ON a.account_id = d.account_id INNER JOIN client AS c ON d.client_id = c.client_id INNER JOIN district AS dist ON c.district_id = dist.district_id WHERE c.gender = 'F' AND c.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F') AND dist.a11 = (SELECT MIN(a11) FROM district AS d INNER JOIN client AS c ON d.district_id = c.district_id WHERE c.gender = 'F' AND c.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F'))

WITH oldestfemaleclients AS (SELECT client_id FROM client WHERE gender = 'F' AND birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F')), lowestavgsalarydistricts AS (SELECT district.district_id, district.a11 FROM client INNER JOIN disp ON client.client_id = disp.client_id INNER JOIN district ON client.district_id = district.district_id WHERE client.gender = 'F' AND client.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F') AND district.a11 = (SELECT MIN(district.a11) FROM client INNER JOIN disp ON client.client_id = disp.client_id INNER JOIN district ON client.district_id = district.district_id WHERE client.gender = 'F' AND client.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F'))) SELECT disp.account_id, (SELECT MAX(a11) - MIN(a11) FROM district) AS gap FROM disp INNER JOIN client ON disp.client_id = client.client_id INNER JOIN district ON client.district_id = district.district_id WHERE client.gender = 'F' AND client.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F') AND district.a11 = (SELECT MIN(district.a11) FROM client INNER JOIN disp ON client.client_id = disp.client_id INNER JOIN district ON client.district_id = district.district_id WHERE client.gender = 'F' AND client.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F'))

WITH lowestavgsalarydistrict AS (SELECT district_id, MIN(a11) AS min_a11 FROM district GROUP BY district_id ORDER BY min_a11 ASC LIMIT 1), oldestfemaleclients AS (SELECT c.client_id, c.birth_date FROM client AS c INNER JOIN lowestavgsalarydistrict AS lsd ON c.district_id = lsd.district_id WHERE c.gender = 'F' ORDER BY c.birth_date ASC LIMIT 1), accountnumbersofoldestfemales AS (SELECT d.account_id FROM disp AS d INNER JOIN oldestfemaleclients AS ofc ON d.client_id = ofc.client_id), salarygap AS (SELECT MAX(a11) - MIN(a11) AS gap FROM district) SELECT anf.account_id, sg.gap FROM accountnumbersofoldestfemales AS anf CROSS JOIN salarygap AS sg

WITH lowestavgsalarydistrict AS (SELECT district_id FROM district WHERE a11 = (SELECT MIN(a11) FROM district)), oldestfemaleclients AS (SELECT c.client_id, c.birth_date FROM client AS c INNER JOIN lowestavgsalarydistrict AS lsd ON c.district_id = lsd.district_id WHERE c.gender = 'F' AND c.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE district_id = lsd.district_id AND gender = 'F')), accountnumbersofoldestfemales AS (SELECT d.account_id FROM disp AS d INNER JOIN oldestfemaleclients AS ofc ON d.client_id = ofc.client_id), salarygap AS (SELECT MAX(a11) - MIN(a11) AS gap FROM district) SELECT anf.account_id, sg.gap FROM accountnumbersofoldestfemales AS anf CROSS JOIN salarygap AS sg

SELECT d.account_id, (SELECT MAX(a11) - MIN(a11) FROM district) AS salary_gap FROM (SELECT disp.account_id FROM disp INNER JOIN client ON disp.client_id = client.client_id WHERE client.gender = 'F' AND client.district_id = (SELECT district_id FROM district ORDER BY a11 ASC LIMIT 1) ORDER BY client.birth_date ASC LIMIT 1) AS d

SELECT a.account_id, (SELECT MAX(a11) FROM district) - (SELECT MIN(a11) FROM district) AS salary_gap FROM account AS a JOIN disp AS d ON a.account_id = d.account_id JOIN client AS c ON d.client_id = c.client_id WHERE c.gender = 'F' AND c.birth_date = (SELECT MAX(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F')

SELECT account.account_id, (SELECT MAX(a11) FROM district) - MIN(district.a11) AS gap FROM disp INNER JOIN client ON disp.client_id = client.client_id INNER JOIN account ON disp.account_id = account.account_id INNER JOIN district ON account.district_id = district.district_id WHERE client.gender = 'F' AND client.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F') AND district.a11 = (SELECT MIN(district.a11) FROM disp INNER JOIN client ON disp.client_id = client.client_id INNER JOIN account ON disp.account_id = account.account_id INNER JOIN district ON account.district_id = district.district_id WHERE client.gender = 'F' AND client.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F'))

SELECT disp.account_id, (SELECT MAX(a11) FROM district) - (SELECT MIN(a11) FROM district WHERE district_id IN (SELECT district_id FROM client WHERE gender = 'F' AND birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F'))) AS gap FROM disp INNER JOIN client ON disp.client_id = client.client_id INNER JOIN district ON client.district_id = district.district_id WHERE client.gender = 'F' AND client.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F') AND district.a11 = (SELECT MIN(a11) FROM district WHERE district_id IN (SELECT district_id FROM client WHERE gender = 'F' AND birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F')))

SELECT disp.account_id, (SELECT MAX(a11) FROM district) - (SELECT MIN(a11) FROM district WHERE district_id IN (SELECT district_id FROM client WHERE gender = 'F' AND birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F'))) AS gap FROM disp INNER JOIN client ON disp.client_id = client.client_id INNER JOIN district ON client.district_id = district.district_id WHERE client.gender = 'F' AND client.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F') AND district.district_id = (SELECT district_id FROM district WHERE a11 = (SELECT MIN(a11) FROM district WHERE district_id IN (SELECT district_id FROM client WHERE gender = 'F' AND birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F'))))

SELECT a.account_id, (SELECT MAX(a11) - MIN(a11) FROM district) AS salary_gap FROM account AS a INNER JOIN disp AS d ON a.account_id = d.account_id INNER JOIN client AS c ON d.client_id = c.client_id WHERE c.gender = 'F' AND c.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F') AND c.district_id = (SELECT d.district_id FROM district AS d INNER JOIN client AS c ON d.district_id = c.district_id WHERE c.gender = 'F' AND c.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F') ORDER BY d.a11 ASC LIMIT 1)

SELECT t2.account_id, (SELECT MAX(a11) FROM district) - (SELECT MIN(a11) FROM district WHERE district_id IN (SELECT district_id FROM client WHERE gender = 'F' AND birth_date = (SELECT birth_date FROM client WHERE gender = 'F' ORDER BY birth_date ASC LIMIT 1))) AS gap FROM client AS t1 INNER JOIN disp AS t2 ON t1.client_id = t2.client_id WHERE t1.gender = 'F' AND t1.birth_date = (SELECT birth_date FROM client WHERE gender = 'F' ORDER BY birth_date ASC LIMIT 1)

SELECT a.account_id, (max_avg_salary - min_avg_salary) AS salary_gap FROM client AS c INNER JOIN disp AS dp ON c.client_id = dp.client_id INNER JOIN account AS a ON dp.account_id = a.account_id INNER JOIN district AS d ON a.district_id = d.district_id CROSS JOIN (SELECT MIN(a11) AS min_avg_salary, MAX(a11) AS max_avg_salary FROM district) AS subquery WHERE c.gender = 'F' AND d.a11 = subquery.min_avg_salary ORDER BY c.birth_date ASC

SELECT a.account_id, (max_avg_salary - min_avg_salary) AS salary_gap FROM client AS c INNER JOIN disp AS dp ON c.client_id = dp.client_id INNER JOIN account AS a ON dp.account_id = a.account_id INNER JOIN district AS d ON a.district_id = d.district_id CROSS JOIN (SELECT MIN(a11) AS min_avg_salary, MAX(a11) AS max_avg_salary FROM district) AS subquery WHERE c.gender = 'F' AND d.a11 = subquery.min_avg_salary AND c.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F' AND district_id = d.district_id AND a11 = subquery.min_avg_salary)

WITH oldest_female_clients AS (SELECT c.client_id, c.birth_date, d.district_id, d.a11 FROM client AS c JOIN disp AS d ON c.client_id = d.client_id JOIN district AS d ON c.district_id = d.district_id WHERE c.gender = 'F' ORDER BY c.birth_date ASC LIMIT 1), lowest_avg_salary_district AS (SELECT ofc.district_id, ofc.a11 FROM oldest_female_clients AS ofc ORDER BY ofc.a11 ASC LIMIT 1) SELECT d.account_id, (SELECT MAX(a11) FROM district) - (SELECT MIN(a11) FROM district) AS salary_gap FROM disp AS d JOIN oldest_female_clients AS ofc ON d.client_id = ofc.client_id JOIN lowest_avg_salary_district AS lasd ON ofc.district_id = lasd.district_id GROUP BY d.account_id

WITH oldestfemaleclients AS (SELECT c.client_id, c.birth_date, d.district_id, d.a11 FROM client AS c INNER JOIN disp AS d ON c.client_id = d.client_id INNER JOIN district AS d ON c.district_id = d.district_id WHERE c.gender = 'F' ORDER BY c.birth_date ASC LIMIT 1), lowestavgsalarydistrict AS (SELECT ofc.district_id, ofc.a11 FROM oldestfemaleclients AS ofc ORDER BY ofc.a11 ASC LIMIT 1), accountnumbers AS (SELECT d.account_id FROM disp AS d INNER JOIN oldestfemaleclients AS ofc ON d.client_id = ofc.client_id INNER JOIN lowestavgsalarydistrict AS lasd ON ofc.district_id = lasd.district_id) SELECT an.account_id, (SELECT MAX(a11) FROM district) - (SELECT MIN(a11) FROM district) AS salary_gap FROM accountnumbers AS an

SELECT c.client_id, (SELECT MAX(a11) - MIN(a11) FROM district) AS salary_gap FROM client AS c INNER JOIN district AS d ON c.district_id = d.district_id WHERE c.gender = 'F' AND d.a11 = (SELECT MIN(a11) FROM district) AND c.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F' AND district_id = d.district_id)

SELECT c.client_id, (SELECT MAX(a11) - MIN(a11) FROM district) AS salary_gap FROM client AS c JOIN district AS d ON c.district_id = d.district_id WHERE c.gender = 'F' AND c.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F')
SELECT c.client_id, (SELECT MAX(a11) - MIN(a11) FROM district) AS salary_gap FROM client AS c WHERE c.gender = 'F' AND c.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F')

SELECT c.client_id, (SELECT MAX(d.a11) - MIN(d.a11) FROM district AS d WHERE d.district_id IN (SELECT c2.district_id FROM client AS c2 WHERE c2.gender = 'F' AND c2.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(c3.birth_date) FROM client AS c3 WHERE c3.gender = 'F'))) AS salary_gap FROM client AS c WHERE c.gender = 'F' AND c.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(c4.birth_date) FROM client AS c4 WHERE c4.gender = 'F') AND c.district_id IN (SELECT d2.district_id FROM district AS d2 WHERE d2.a11 = (SELECT MIN(d3.a11) FROM district AS d3 WHERE d3.district_id IN (SELECT c5.district_id FROM client AS c5 WHERE c5.gender = 'F' AND c5.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(c6.birth_date) FROM client AS c6 WHERE c6.gender = 'F'))))

SELECT a.account_id, (SELECT MAX(a11) - MIN(a11) FROM district) AS salary_gap FROM account AS a INNER JOIN disp AS d ON a.account_id = d.account_id INNER JOIN client AS c ON d.client_id = c.client_id WHERE c.gender = 'F' AND c.district_id = (SELECT district_id FROM district ORDER BY a11 ASC LIMIT 1) ORDER BY c.birth_date ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT t3.account_id, (SELECT MAX(a11) - MIN(a11) FROM district) AS salary_gap FROM (SELECT client_id, birth_date FROM client WHERE gender = 'F' AND district_id = (SELECT district_id FROM district WHERE a11 = (SELECT MIN(a11) FROM district))) AS t2 INNER JOIN disp AS t3 ON t2.client_id = t3.client_id WHERE t2.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM (SELECT client_id, birth_date FROM client WHERE gender = 'F' AND district_id = (SELECT district_id FROM district WHERE a11 = (SELECT MIN(a11) FROM district))))

SELECT t3.account_id, (SELECT MAX(a11) - MIN(a11) FROM district) AS salary_gap FROM (SELECT client_id, birth_date FROM client WHERE gender = 'F' AND district_id = (SELECT district_id FROM district WHERE a11 = (SELECT MIN(a11) FROM district)) AND birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F' AND district_id = (SELECT district_id FROM district WHERE a11 = (SELECT MIN(a11) FROM district)))) AS t2 INNER JOIN disp AS t3 ON t2.client_id = t3.client_id

SELECT d.account_id, (SELECT MAX(a11) - MIN(a11) FROM district) AS salary_gap FROM disp AS d JOIN client AS c ON d.client_id = c.client_id JOIN district AS dist ON c.district_id = dist.district_id WHERE c.gender = 'F' AND c.district_id = (SELECT district_id FROM district ORDER BY a11 ASC LIMIT 1) ORDER BY c.birth_date ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT d."account_id", (SELECT MAX("A11") - MIN("A11") FROM "district") AS "salary_gap" FROM (SELECT "disp"."account_id", "client"."district_id" FROM "disp" INNER JOIN "client" ON "disp"."client_id" = "client"."client_id" WHERE "client"."gender" = 'F' ORDER BY "client"."birth_date" ASC LIMIT 1) AS d INNER JOIN (SELECT "district_id", "A11" FROM "district" WHERE "district_id" = (SELECT "district_id" FROM "client" WHERE "gender" = 'F' ORDER BY "birth_date" ASC LIMIT 1) ORDER BY "A11" ASC LIMIT 1) AS dist ON d."district_id" = dist."district_id"

SELECT t2.account_id, (SELECT MAX(a11) FROM district) - (SELECT MIN(a11) FROM district WHERE district_id IN (SELECT t1.district_id FROM client AS t1 WHERE t1.gender = 'F' AND t1.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F'))) AS salary_gap FROM client AS t1 INNER JOIN disp AS t2 ON t1.client_id = t2.client_id WHERE t1.gender = 'F' AND t1.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F')

SELECT disp.account_id, (SELECT MAX(district.a11) - MIN(district.a11) FROM district) AS salary_gap FROM disp INNER JOIN client ON disp.client_id = client.client_id INNER JOIN district ON client.district_id = district.district_id WHERE client.gender = 'F' AND district.a11 = (SELECT MIN(district.a11) FROM district) ORDER BY client.birth_date ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT disp.account_id, (SELECT MAX(district.a11) - MIN(district.a11) FROM district) AS salary_gap FROM disp INNER JOIN client ON disp.client_id = client.client_id INNER JOIN district ON client.district_id = district.district_id WHERE client.gender = 'F' AND district.a11 = (SELECT MIN(district.a11) FROM district) ORDER BY client.birth_date ASC LIMIT 1

1011.sql: SELECT t1.forename, t1.surname FROM drivers AS t1 INNER JOIN laptimes AS t2 ON t1.driverid = t2.driverid ORDER BY t2.time ASC LIMIT 20
SELECT t1.forename, t1.surname FROM drivers AS t1 INNER JOIN laptimes AS t2 ON t1.driverid = t2.driverid WHERE t2.time = (SELECT MIN(time) FROM laptimes) LIMIT 20

SELECT d.forename, d.surname FROM drivers AS d INNER JOIN (SELECT raceid, driverid, lap FROM laptimes WHERE CAST(SUBSTRING(time, 1, INSTR(time, ':') - 1) AS INTEGER) * 60000 + CAST(SUBSTRING(time, INSTR(time, ':') + 1, INSTR(time, '.') - INSTR(time, ':') - 1) AS INTEGER) * 1000 + CAST(SUBSTRING(time, INSTR(time, '.') + 1) AS INTEGER) = (SELECT MIN(time_in_milliseconds) FROM (SELECT CAST(SUBSTRING(time, 1, INSTR(time, ':') - 1) AS INTEGER) * 60000 + CAST(SUBSTRING(time, INSTR(time, ':') + 1, INSTR(time, '.') - INSTR(time, ':') - 1) AS INTEGER) * 1000 + CAST(SUBSTRING(time, INSTR(time, '.') + 1) AS INTEGER) AS time_in_milliseconds FROM laptimes))) AS lt ON d.driverid = lt.driverid LIMIT 20

SELECT t1.forename, t1.surname FROM drivers AS t1 INNER JOIN (SELECT driverid, MIN(milliseconds) AS min_milliseconds FROM laptimes GROUP BY driverid ORDER BY min_milliseconds ASC LIMIT 20) AS t2 ON t1.driverid = t2.driverid
SELECT t1.forename, t1.surname FROM drivers AS t1 INNER JOIN laptimes AS t2 ON t1.driverid = t2.driverid WHERE t2.milliseconds = (SELECT MIN(milliseconds) FROM laptimes) LIMIT 20

SELECT DISTINCT d.forename, d.surname FROM drivers AS d INNER JOIN laptimes AS l ON d.driverid = l.driverid WHERE l.milliseconds = (SELECT MIN(milliseconds) FROM laptimes) ORDER BY l.milliseconds ASC LIMIT 20

SELECT d.forename, d.surname FROM laptimes AS l INNER JOIN drivers AS d ON l.driverid = d.driverid ORDER BY CAST(SUBSTRING(l.time, 1, INSTR(l.time, ':') - 1) AS INTEGER) * 60 + CAST(SUBSTRING(l.time, INSTR(l.time, ':') + 1) AS REAL) ASC LIMIT 20
SELECT DISTINCT d.forename, d.surname FROM laptimes AS l INNER JOIN drivers AS d ON l.driverid = d.driverid ORDER BY l.time ASC LIMIT 20

SELECT DISTINCT d.forename, d.surname FROM drivers AS d INNER JOIN (SELECT driverid, MIN(CAST(SUBSTRING(time, 1, INSTR(time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 60 + CAST(SUBSTRING(time, INSTR(time, ':') + 1, INSTR(time, '.') - INSTR(time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) + CAST(SUBSTRING(time, INSTR(time, '.') + 1) AS REAL) / 1000) AS min_time FROM laptimes GROUP BY driverid ORDER BY min_time ASC LIMIT 20) AS lt ON d.driverid = lt.driverid

880.sql: SELECT ((r853.fastestlapspeed - r854.fastestlapspeed) / r853.fastestlapspeed) * 100 AS percentage_difference FROM (SELECT fastestlapspeed FROM results WHERE driverid = (SELECT driverid FROM drivers WHERE forename = 'Paul' AND surname = 'di Resta') AND raceid = 853) AS r853 CROSS JOIN (SELECT fastestlapspeed FROM results WHERE driverid = (SELECT driverid FROM drivers WHERE forename = 'Paul' AND surname = 'di Resta') AND raceid = 854) AS r854

SELECT ((CAST(r1.fastestlapspeed AS REAL) - CAST(r2.fastestlapspeed AS REAL)) / CAST(r1.fastestlapspeed AS REAL)) * 100 AS percent_faster FROM (SELECT fastestlapspeed FROM results WHERE raceid = 853 AND driverid = (SELECT driverid FROM drivers WHERE forename = 'Paul' AND surname = 'di Resta')) AS r1 CROSS JOIN (SELECT fastestlapspeed FROM results WHERE raceid = 854 AND driverid = (SELECT driverid FROM drivers WHERE forename = 'Paul' AND surname = 'di Resta')) AS r2

SELECT ((CAST(r1.fastestlapspeed AS REAL) - CAST(r2.fastestlapspeed AS REAL)) / CAST(r1.fastestlapspeed AS REAL)) * 100 AS percent_faster FROM results AS r1 JOIN drivers AS d ON r1.driverid = d.driverid JOIN races AS ra1 ON r1.raceid = ra1.raceid JOIN results AS r2 ON ra1.raceid + 1 = r2.raceid JOIN races AS ra2 ON r2.raceid = ra2.raceid WHERE d.forename = 'Paul' AND d.surname = 'di Resta' AND ra1.raceid = 853 AND ra2.raceid = 854

SELECT ((t1.fastestlapspeed - t2.fastestlapspeed) * 100.0 / t1.fastestlapspeed) AS percentage_faster FROM (SELECT fastestlapspeed FROM results WHERE raceid = 853 AND driverid = (SELECT driverid FROM drivers WHERE forename = 'Paul' AND surname = 'di Resta')) AS t1 CROSS JOIN (SELECT MIN(fastestlapspeed) AS fastestlapspeed FROM results WHERE raceid = 854) AS t2

SELECT ((t1.fastestlapspeed - t2.fastestlapspeed) * 100.0 / t1.fastestlapspeed) AS percentage_faster FROM (SELECT fastestlapspeed FROM results WHERE raceid = 853 AND driverid = (SELECT driverid FROM drivers WHERE forename = 'Paul' AND surname = 'di Resta')) AS t1 CROSS JOIN (SELECT fastestlapspeed FROM results WHERE raceid = 854 ORDER BY fastestlapspeed ASC LIMIT 1) AS t2

SELECT ((CAST(race_853.fastestlapspeed AS REAL) - CAST(race_854.fastestlapspeed AS REAL)) / CAST(race_853.fastestlapspeed AS REAL)) * 100 AS percentage_difference FROM (SELECT fastestlapspeed FROM results INNER JOIN drivers ON results.driverid = drivers.driverid WHERE drivers.forename = 'Paul' AND drivers.surname = 'di Resta' AND results.raceid = 853) AS race_853 CROSS JOIN (SELECT fastestlapspeed FROM results INNER JOIN drivers ON results.driverid = drivers.driverid WHERE drivers.forename = 'Paul' AND drivers.surname = 'di Resta' AND results.raceid = 854) AS race_854

SELECT ((race_853.fastestlapspeed - race_854.fastestlapspeed) * 100) / race_853.fastestlapspeed AS percentagedifference FROM (SELECT fastestlapspeed FROM results AS r INNER JOIN drivers AS d ON r.driverid = d.driverid WHERE d.forename = 'Paul' AND d.surname = 'di Resta' AND r.raceid = 853) AS race_853 CROSS JOIN (SELECT fastestlapspeed FROM results WHERE raceid = 854 ORDER BY fastestlapspeed DESC LIMIT 1) AS race_854

SELECT races.year, AVG(CAST(SUBSTRING(results.time, 1, INSTR(results.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 3600 + CAST(SUBSTRING(results.time, INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(results.time, INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(results.time, INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1 - 1) - INSTR(results.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 60 + CAST(SUBSTRING(results.time, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(results.time, INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(results.time, INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1 - 1) + 1) AS REAL)) AS avg_time_seconds FROM results INNER JOIN races ON results.raceid = races.raceid WHERE results.time LIKE '%:%:%.%' AND races.year < 1975 GROUP BY races.year

SELECT races.year, AVG(CAST(SUBSTRING(results.time, 1, INSTR(results.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 3600 + CAST(SUBSTRING(results.time, INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(results.time, INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(results.time, INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1 - 1) - INSTR(results.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 60 + CAST(REPLACE(SUBSTRING(results.time, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(results.time, INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(results.time, INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1 - 1) + 1), '.', '') AS REAL) / 1000) AS avg_time_seconds FROM results INNER JOIN races ON results.raceid = races.raceid WHERE results.time LIKE '%:%:%.%' AND races.year < 1975 GROUP BY races.year

SELECT races.year, AVG(STRFTIME('%M', results.time) * 60 + STRFTIME('%S', results.time) + CAST(SUBSTRING(results.time, INSTR(results.time, '.') + 1) AS REAL) / 1000) AS average_time_seconds FROM results INNER JOIN races ON results.raceid = races.raceid WHERE results.time LIKE '%:%:%.%' AND NOT results.time IS NULL AND races.year < 1975 GROUP BY races.year

SELECT r.year, AVG(CASE WHEN res.time LIKE '%:%:%' THEN CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, 1, INSTR(res.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 3600 + CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 60 + CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') + 1) AS REAL) WHEN res.time LIKE '%:%' THEN CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, 1, INSTR(res.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 60 + CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1) AS REAL) ELSE CAST(res.time AS REAL) END) AS avg_time_in_seconds FROM races AS r INNER JOIN results AS res ON r.raceid = res.raceid WHERE r.year < 1975 AND res.position = 1 GROUP BY r.year

SELECT r.year, AVG((CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, 1, INSTR(res.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 3600 + CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1 - 1) - INSTR(res.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 60 + CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1 - 1) + 1, INSTR(res.time, '.') - IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1 - 1) - 1) AS REAL))) AS avg_total_seconds FROM races AS r INNER JOIN results AS res ON r.raceid = res.raceid WHERE r.year < 1975 AND res.time LIKE '%:%:%.%' GROUP BY r.year

SELECT races.year, AVG(CAST(SUBSTRING(results.time, 1, INSTR(results.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 3600 + CAST(SUBSTRING(results.time, INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(results.time, INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(results.time, INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1 - 1) - INSTR(results.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 60 + CAST(SUBSTRING(results.time, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(results.time, INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(results.time, INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1 - 1) + 1) AS REAL)) AS avg_time_seconds FROM results INNER JOIN races ON results.raceid = races.raceid WHERE results.position = 1 AND races.year < 1975 GROUP BY races.year

SELECT races.year, AVG(CAST(SUBSTRING(results.time, 1, INSTR(results.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 3600 + CAST(SUBSTRING(results.time, INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(results.time, INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(results.time, INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1 - 1) - INSTR(results.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 60 + CAST(SUBSTRING(results.time, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(results.time, INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(results.time, INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1 - 1) + 1) AS REAL)) AS avg_time_seconds FROM results INNER JOIN races ON results.raceid = races.raceid WHERE results.position = 1 AND races.year < 1975 GROUP BY races.year

SELECT r.year, AVG(CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, 1, INSTR(res.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 3600 + CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1 - 1) - INSTR(res.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 60 + CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1 - 1) + 1) AS REAL)) AS avg_champion_time_seconds FROM results AS res INNER JOIN races AS r ON res.raceid = r.raceid WHERE NOT res.time LIKE '+%' AND r.year < 1975 GROUP BY r.year

SELECT r.year, AVG(CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, 1, INSTR(res.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 3600 + CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1 - 1) - INSTR(res.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 60 + CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1 - 1) + 1) AS REAL)) AS avg_time_in_seconds FROM races AS r INNER JOIN results AS res ON r.raceid = res.raceid WHERE r.year < 1975 AND res.position = 1 GROUP BY r.year

SELECT r.year, AVG(CASE WHEN res.time LIKE '%:%:%.%' THEN CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, 1, INSTR(res.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 3600 + CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1 - 1) - INSTR(res.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 60 + CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1 - 1) + 1, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1 - 1) + 1), '.') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1 - 1) + 1), '.') + IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1 - 1) + 1 - 1) - IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1 - 1) - 1) AS REAL) + CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, '.') + 1) AS REAL) / 1000 WHEN res.time LIKE '%:%.%' THEN CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, 1, INSTR(res.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 60 + CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), '.') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), '.') + INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1 - 1) - INSTR(res.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) + CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, '.') + 1) AS REAL) / 1000 ELSE CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, 1, INSTR(res.time, '.') - 1) AS REAL) + CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, '.') + 1) AS REAL) / 1000 END) AS avg_time_seconds FROM races AS r INNER JOIN results AS res ON r.raceid = res.raceid WHERE r.year < 1975 AND res.position = 1 AND NOT res.time IS NULL GROUP BY r.year

SELECT r.year, AVG(CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, 1, INSTR(res.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 3600 + CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1 - 1) - INSTR(res.time, ':') - 1) AS REAL) * 60 + CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1 - 1) + 1, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1 - 1) + 1), '.') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1 - 1) + 1), '.') + IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1 - 1) + 1 - 1) - IIF(INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') = 0, 0, INSTR(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1), ':') + INSTR(res.time, ':') + 1 - 1) - 1) AS REAL) + CAST(SUBSTRING(res.time, INSTR(res.time, '.') + 1) AS REAL) / 1000) AS avg_time_seconds FROM races AS r INNER JOIN results AS res ON r.raceid = res.raceid WHERE r.year < 1975 AND res.position = 1 AND NOT res.time IS NULL GROUP BY r.year

1016.sql: SELECT SUM(pitstops.duration) FROM pitstops INNER JOIN races ON pitstops.raceid = races.raceid INNER JOIN laptimes ON pitstops.raceid = laptimes.raceid AND pitstops.driverid = laptimes.driverid WHERE races.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' ORDER BY laptimes.milliseconds ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT SUM(pitstops.duration) AS total_pit_stop_duration FROM pitstops INNER JOIN races ON pitstops.raceid = races.raceid WHERE pitstops.driverid = (SELECT laptimes.driverid FROM laptimes INNER JOIN races ON laptimes.raceid = races.raceid WHERE races.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' ORDER BY laptimes.milliseconds ASC LIMIT 1) AND races.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix'

SELECT SUM(t3.duration) AS total_pit_stop_duration FROM races AS t1 INNER JOIN laptimes AS t2 ON t1.raceid = t2.raceid INNER JOIN pitstops AS t3 ON t2.raceid = t3.raceid AND t2.driverid = t3.driverid WHERE t1.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' AND t2.milliseconds = (SELECT MIN(milliseconds) FROM laptimes WHERE raceid = t1.raceid)

SELECT SUM(t3.duration) AS total_pit_stop_duration FROM races AS t1 INNER JOIN laptimes AS t2 ON t1.raceid = t2.raceid INNER JOIN pitstops AS t3 ON t2.raceid = t3.raceid AND t2.driverid = t3.driverid WHERE t1.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' ORDER BY t2.milliseconds ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT SUM(p.duration) AS total_pit_stop_duration FROM races AS r INNER JOIN laptimes AS l ON r.raceid = l.raceid INNER JOIN pitstops AS p ON r.raceid = p.raceid AND l.driverid = p.driverid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' AND l.time = (SELECT MIN(time) FROM laptimes WHERE raceid = r.raceid)

SELECT SUM(p.duration) AS total_pit_stop_duration FROM races AS r INNER JOIN laptimes AS l ON r.raceid = l.raceid INNER JOIN pitstops AS p ON r.raceid = p.raceid AND l.driverid = p.driverid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' GROUP BY l.driverid, l.time ORDER BY l.time ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT ps.duration FROM pitstops AS ps INNER JOIN races AS r ON ps.raceid = r.raceid INNER JOIN laptimes AS lt ON ps.raceid = lt.raceid AND ps.driverid = lt.driverid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' AND lt.milliseconds = (SELECT MIN(milliseconds) FROM laptimes WHERE raceid = r.raceid) AND lt.driverid = (SELECT driverid FROM laptimes WHERE raceid = r.raceid ORDER BY milliseconds ASC LIMIT 1)

SELECT ps.duration FROM pitstops AS ps INNER JOIN races AS r ON ps.raceid = r.raceid INNER JOIN laptimes AS lt ON ps.raceid = lt.raceid AND ps.driverid = lt.driverid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' AND lt.milliseconds = (SELECT MIN(milliseconds) FROM laptimes WHERE raceid = r.raceid)

SELECT SUM(ps.duration) AS total_pit_stop_duration FROM pitstops AS ps INNER JOIN laptimes AS lt ON ps.raceid = lt.raceid AND ps.driverid = lt.driverid INNER JOIN races AS r ON lt.raceid = r.raceid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' GROUP BY ps.driverid ORDER BY lt.time ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT ps.duration FROM pitstops AS ps INNER JOIN races AS r ON ps.raceid = r.raceid INNER JOIN laptimes AS lt ON ps.raceid = lt.raceid AND ps.driverid = lt.driverid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' AND lt.time = (SELECT MIN(time) FROM laptimes WHERE raceid = r.raceid)

SELECT ps.duration FROM races AS r INNER JOIN laptimes AS lt ON r.raceid = lt.raceid INNER JOIN pitstops AS ps ON lt.raceid = ps.raceid AND lt.driverid = ps.driverid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' AND lt.time = (SELECT MIN(time) FROM laptimes WHERE raceid = r.raceid)

SELECT ps.duration FROM pitstops AS ps INNER JOIN races AS r ON ps.raceid = r.raceid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' AND ps.driverid = (SELECT lt.driverid FROM laptimes AS lt INNER JOIN races AS r ON lt.raceid = r.raceid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' ORDER BY lt.milliseconds ASC LIMIT 1) LIMIT 1

SELECT ps.duration FROM pitstops AS ps INNER JOIN races AS r ON ps.raceid = r.raceid INNER JOIN laptimes AS lt ON ps.raceid = lt.raceid AND ps.driverid = lt.driverid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' ORDER BY lt.milliseconds ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT ps.duration FROM races AS r INNER JOIN pitstops AS ps ON r.raceid = ps.raceid INNER JOIN (SELECT raceid, driverid, MIN(time) AS fastest_lap_time FROM laptimes WHERE raceid IN (SELECT raceid FROM races WHERE name = 'Austrian Grand Prix') GROUP BY raceid, driverid) AS fl ON r.raceid = fl.raceid AND ps.driverid = fl.driverid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' AND fl.fastest_lap_time = (SELECT MIN(time) FROM laptimes WHERE raceid IN (SELECT raceid FROM races WHERE name = 'Austrian Grand Prix'))

SELECT pitstops.duration FROM races INNER JOIN pitstops ON races.raceid = pitstops.raceid INNER JOIN (SELECT raceid, MIN(time) AS fastest_lap_time FROM laptimes WHERE raceid IN (SELECT raceid FROM races WHERE name = 'Austrian Grand Prix') GROUP BY raceid) AS fastestlaps ON pitstops.raceid = fastestlaps.raceid WHERE races.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix'

SELECT t3.duration FROM races AS t1 INNER JOIN laptimes AS t2 ON t1.raceid = t2.raceid INNER JOIN pitstops AS t3 ON t2.raceid = t3.raceid AND t2.driverid = t3.driverid WHERE t1.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' ORDER BY t2.time ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT SUM(ps.duration) AS total_pit_stop_duration FROM races AS r INNER JOIN laptimes AS lt ON r.raceid = lt.raceid INNER JOIN pitstops AS ps ON r.raceid = ps.raceid AND lt.driverid = ps.driverid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' AND lt.driverid = (SELECT driverid FROM laptimes WHERE raceid = r.raceid ORDER BY time ASC LIMIT 1)

SELECT SUM(ps.duration) AS total_pit_stop_duration FROM races AS r INNER JOIN laptimes AS lt ON r.raceid = lt.raceid INNER JOIN pitstops AS ps ON r.raceid = ps.raceid AND lt.driverid = ps.driverid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' AND lt.time = (SELECT MIN(time) FROM laptimes WHERE raceid = r.raceid)

SELECT ps.duration FROM circuits AS c INNER JOIN races AS r ON c.circuitid = r.circuitid INNER JOIN laptimes AS lt ON r.raceid = lt.raceid INNER JOIN pitstops AS ps ON lt.raceid = ps.raceid AND lt.driverid = ps.driverid WHERE c.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' AND lt.time = (SELECT MIN(time) FROM laptimes WHERE raceid = r.raceid)

SELECT ps.duration FROM pitstops AS ps JOIN (SELECT lt.raceid, lt.driverid FROM laptimes AS lt JOIN (SELECT r.raceid FROM races AS r JOIN circuits AS c ON r.circuitid = c.circuitid WHERE c.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix Circuit') AS rc ON lt.raceid = rc.raceid ORDER BY lt.time ASC LIMIT 1) AS fd ON ps.raceid = fd.raceid AND ps.driverid = fd.driverid

SELECT SUM(pitstops.duration) FROM pitstops INNER JOIN races ON pitstops.raceid = races.raceid INNER JOIN laptimes ON pitstops.raceid = laptimes.raceid AND pitstops.driverid = laptimes.driverid WHERE races.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' ORDER BY laptimes.time ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT SUM(pitstops.duration) FROM pitstops INNER JOIN races ON pitstops.raceid = races.raceid WHERE races.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' AND pitstops.driverid = (SELECT laptimes.driverid FROM laptimes INNER JOIN races ON laptimes.raceid = races.raceid WHERE races.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' ORDER BY laptimes.time ASC LIMIT 1)

SELECT SUM(pitstops.duration) AS total_pit_stop_duration FROM races INNER JOIN laptimes ON races.raceid = laptimes.raceid INNER JOIN pitstops ON laptimes.raceid = pitstops.raceid AND laptimes.driverid = pitstops.driverid WHERE races.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' AND laptimes.milliseconds = (SELECT MIN(milliseconds) FROM laptimes WHERE raceid = races.raceid)

SELECT ps.duration FROM pitstops AS ps INNER JOIN (SELECT lt.raceid, lt.driverid FROM laptimes AS lt INNER JOIN races AS r ON lt.raceid = r.raceid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' ORDER BY lt.time ASC LIMIT 1) AS fastest_lap ON ps.raceid = fastest_lap.raceid AND ps.driverid = fastest_lap.driverid

SELECT SUM(ps.duration) AS total_pit_stop_duration FROM races AS r JOIN laptimes AS lt ON r.raceid = lt.raceid JOIN pitstops AS ps ON r.raceid = ps.raceid AND lt.driverid = ps.driverid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' AND lt.driverid = (SELECT driverid FROM laptimes WHERE raceid = r.raceid ORDER BY time ASC LIMIT 1)

SELECT SUM(ps.duration) AS total_pit_stop_duration FROM races AS r JOIN laptimes AS lt ON r.raceid = lt.raceid JOIN pitstops AS ps ON r.raceid = ps.raceid AND lt.driverid = ps.driverid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' AND lt.time = (SELECT MIN(time) FROM laptimes WHERE raceid = r.raceid)

SELECT pitstops.duration FROM pitstops WHERE pitstops.raceid = (SELECT races.raceid FROM races INNER JOIN circuits ON races.circuitid = circuits.circuitid WHERE circuits.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix Circuit') AND pitstops.driverid = (SELECT laptimes.driverid FROM laptimes WHERE laptimes.raceid = (SELECT races.raceid FROM races INNER JOIN circuits ON races.circuitid = circuits.circuitid WHERE circuits.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix Circuit') AND laptimes.time = (SELECT MIN(laptimes.time) FROM laptimes WHERE laptimes.raceid = (SELECT races.raceid FROM races INNER JOIN circuits ON races.circuitid = circuits.circuitid WHERE circuits.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix Circuit')))

SELECT SUM(t3.duration) AS total_pit_stop_duration FROM races AS t1 INNER JOIN laptimes AS t2 ON t1.raceid = t2.raceid INNER JOIN pitstops AS t3 ON t1.raceid = t3.raceid AND t2.driverid = t3.driverid WHERE t1.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' AND t2.milliseconds = (SELECT MIN(milliseconds) FROM laptimes AS t4 INNER JOIN races AS t5 ON t4.raceid = t5.raceid WHERE t5.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix')

SELECT ps.duration FROM pitstops AS ps INNER JOIN laptimes AS lt ON ps.raceid = lt.raceid AND ps.driverid = lt.driverid INNER JOIN races AS r ON lt.raceid = r.raceid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' ORDER BY lt.milliseconds ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT ps.duration FROM pitstops AS ps INNER JOIN races AS r ON ps.raceid = r.raceid INNER JOIN laptimes AS lt ON ps.raceid = lt.raceid AND ps.driverid = lt.driverid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' ORDER BY lt.milliseconds ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT SUM(ps.duration) FROM pitstops AS ps INNER JOIN races AS r ON ps.raceid = r.raceid INNER JOIN (SELECT lt.driverid, lt.raceid, lt.time FROM laptimes AS lt INNER JOIN races AS r ON lt.raceid = r.raceid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' ORDER BY lt.time ASC LIMIT 1) AS fastest_lap ON ps.raceid = fastest_lap.raceid AND ps.driverid = fastest_lap.driverid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix'

SELECT ps.duration FROM pitstops AS ps INNER JOIN races AS r ON ps.raceid = r.raceid INNER JOIN (SELECT driverid, raceid, MIN(time) AS min_time FROM laptimes GROUP BY driverid, raceid) AS lt ON ps.driverid = lt.driverid AND ps.raceid = lt.raceid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' ORDER BY lt.min_time ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT ps.duration FROM pitstops AS ps INNER JOIN races AS r ON ps.raceid = r.raceid INNER JOIN laptimes AS lt ON ps.driverid = lt.driverid AND ps.raceid = lt.raceid WHERE r.name = 'Austrian Grand Prix' AND lt.time = (SELECT MIN(time) FROM laptimes WHERE raceid = r.raceid) LIMIT 1

1001.sql: SELECT t3.forename, t3.surname FROM qualifying AS t1 INNER JOIN races AS t2 ON t1.raceid = t2.raceid INNER JOIN drivers AS t3 ON t1.driverid = t3.driverid INNER JOIN results AS t4 ON t1.raceid = t4.raceid AND t1.driverid = t4.driverid WHERE t2.name = 'Marina Bay Street Circuit' AND t2.year = 2008 AND t4.position = 1 ORDER BY t1.q3 ASC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 2

SELECT t3.forename, t3.surname FROM races AS t1 INNER JOIN qualifying AS t2 ON t1.raceid = t2.raceid INNER JOIN drivers AS t3 ON t2.driverid = t3.driverid INNER JOIN circuits AS t4 ON t1.circuitid = t4.circuitid WHERE t1.year = 2008 AND t4.name = 'Marina Bay Street Circuit' AND t2.position = 1 ORDER BY t2.q3 ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT forename, surname FROM drivers WHERE driverid = (SELECT driverid FROM qualifying WHERE qualifyid = (SELECT qualifyid FROM qualifying WHERE raceid = (SELECT raceid FROM races INNER JOIN circuits ON races.circuitid = circuits.circuitid WHERE circuits.name = 'Marina Bay Street Circuit' AND races.year = 2008) ORDER BY qualifyid LIMIT 1 OFFSET 2) ORDER BY q3 LIMIT 1)

SELECT d.forename, d.surname FROM qualifying AS q INNER JOIN drivers AS d ON q.driverid = d.driverid INNER JOIN races AS r ON q.raceid = r.raceid INNER JOIN circuits AS c ON r.circuitid = c.circuitid WHERE c.name = 'Marina Bay Street Circuit' AND r.year = 2008 ORDER BY q.q3 ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT t3.forename, t3.surname FROM (SELECT driverid FROM qualifying WHERE raceid = (SELECT raceid FROM races INNER JOIN circuits ON races.circuitid = circuits.circuitid WHERE races.year = 2008 AND races.round = 3 AND circuits.name = 'Marina Bay Street Circuit') ORDER BY q3 LIMIT 1) AS t2 INNER JOIN drivers AS t3 ON t2.driverid = t3.driverid

SELECT d.forename, d.surname FROM drivers AS d INNER JOIN qualifying AS q ON d.driverid = q.driverid INNER JOIN races AS r ON q.raceid = r.raceid INNER JOIN circuits AS c ON r.circuitid = c.circuitid WHERE r.year = 2008 AND r.round = 3 AND c.name = 'Marina Bay Street Circuit' ORDER BY q.q3 LIMIT 1

SELECT d.forename, d.surname FROM drivers AS d INNER JOIN qualifying AS q ON d.driverid = q.driverid INNER JOIN races AS r ON q.raceid = r.raceid INNER JOIN circuits AS c ON r.circuitid = c.circuitid WHERE r.year = 2008 AND r.round = 3 AND c.name = 'Marina Bay Street Circuit' ORDER BY q.q3 LIMIT 1

SELECT t3.forename, t3.surname FROM qualifying AS t1 INNER JOIN races AS t2 ON t1.raceid = t2.raceid INNER JOIN drivers AS t3 ON t1.driverid = t3.driverid INNER JOIN circuits AS t4 ON t2.circuitid = t4.circuitid WHERE t2.year = 2008 AND t4.name = 'Marina Bay Street Circuit' ORDER BY t1.q3 LIMIT 1 OFFSET 2

SELECT t3.forename, t3.surname FROM qualifying AS t1 INNER JOIN races AS t2 ON t1.raceid = t2.raceid INNER JOIN drivers AS t3 ON t1.driverid = t3.driverid INNER JOIN circuits AS t4 ON t2.circuitid = t4.circuitid WHERE t2.year = 2008 AND t4.name = 'Marina Bay Street Circuit' AND t1.raceid = (SELECT raceid FROM qualifying INNER JOIN races ON qualifying.raceid = races.raceid INNER JOIN circuits ON races.circuitid = circuits.circuitid WHERE races.year = 2008 AND circuits.name = 'Marina Bay Street Circuit' ORDER BY qualifying.raceid LIMIT 1 OFFSET 2) ORDER BY t1.q3 ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT d.forename, d.surname FROM qualifying AS q INNER JOIN races AS r ON q.raceid = r.raceid INNER JOIN circuits AS c ON r.circuitid = c.circuitid INNER JOIN drivers AS d ON q.driverid = d.driverid WHERE r.year = 2008 AND c.name = 'Marina Bay Street Circuit' ORDER BY q.q3 ASC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 2

SELECT drivers.forename, drivers.surname FROM drivers WHERE drivers.driverid = (SELECT qualifying.driverid FROM qualifying WHERE qualifying.raceid = (SELECT races.raceid FROM races INNER JOIN circuits ON races.circuitid = circuits.circuitid WHERE races.year = 2008 AND races.round = 3 AND circuits.name = 'Marina Bay Street Circuit') ORDER BY qualifying.q3 ASC LIMIT 1)

SELECT t1.forename, t1.surname FROM drivers AS t1 INNER JOIN qualifying AS t2 ON t1.driverid = t2.driverid INNER JOIN races AS t3 ON t2.raceid = t3.raceid INNER JOIN circuits AS t4 ON t3.circuitid = t4.circuitid WHERE t3.year = 2008 AND t3.round = 3 AND t4.name = 'Marina Bay Street Circuit' ORDER BY t2.q3 ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT t1.forename, t1.surname FROM drivers AS t1 INNER JOIN qualifying AS t2 ON t1.driverid = t2.driverid INNER JOIN races AS t3 ON t2.raceid = t3.raceid INNER JOIN circuits AS t4 ON t3.circuitid = t4.circuitid WHERE t3.year = 2008 AND t4.name = 'Marina Bay Street Circuit' ORDER BY t2.q3 ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT drivers.forename, drivers.surname FROM qualifying INNER JOIN drivers ON qualifying.driverid = drivers.driverid INNER JOIN races ON qualifying.raceid = races.raceid INNER JOIN circuits ON races.circuitid = circuits.circuitid WHERE qualifying.position = 1 AND races.year = 2008 AND circuits.name = 'Marina Bay Street Circuit'
